{"tid":627983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"即日玩得　Birdie 自由鳥率先推出「7」字頭電話號碼","createTime":"2018-04-13T12:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T12:26:35.000Z","uid":143760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3f630c90323cf4a5de229becaed9502fdef967","tid":627983,"uid":143760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"今年年初說好推出的「8」字頭電話號碼至今仍未推出。Birdie 自由鳥今天宣佈率先推出「7」字頭電話號碼，即日起已經可以在 Birdie APP 選用，小編嘗試抽號碼都抽到『7071 0701』，不過手快再更新號碼因此錯過了&hellip;想用新「7」字頭電話號碼的讀者可以下載 Birdie 並購買電話卡盡快註冊個「7」靚號碼啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/04/13/birdie-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2Fbirdie-2%2F&d=Voc7XZDaq3ERB9ldoR2bIZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2252be5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/04/13/birdie-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/201210_ac082acd2db5b1e38b96f58b1c676a4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F201210_ac082acd2db5b1e38b96f58b1c676a4c.jpg&h=4e8f325f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13a23490dcfb7626a38c6eb277c8d3e45b0298c2","tid":627983,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:16:16.000Z","msg":"吓？有咩好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e674f81007845f8904f32e27eb77d2894a4374e","tid":627983,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13a23490dcfb7626a38c6eb277c8d3e45b0298c2","tid":627983,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:16:16.000Z","msg":"吓？有咩好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:20:16.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n仲有人記電話號碼？"},{"pid":"8475b607fd577964f0c0828fef29a97d9aad207f","tid":627983,"uid":143760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e674f81007845f8904f3